---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/Sections/PageHeader.astro";
import StaffList from "../components/Sections/StaffList.astro";
import { Carousel } from 'webcoreui/astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Coaching | Ariane Mader"
  seoTitle="Coaching & Counselling | Procrastination, Overwhelm, Habits & Career Clarity"
  description="Practical, reflective coaching and counselling for procrastination, overwhelm, habits, neurodivergence, and career or study clarity."
  canonicalUrl="https://arianemader.com/coaching"
  lang="en"
>
  <PageHeader 
    title="Coaching & Counselling" 
    backgroundImage="/uploads/coaching-header.jpg"
    overlayOpacity={0.15}
  />
  
  <!-- Staff List -->
  <!-- <StaffList /> -->

<!-- What we can work on together -->
<section id="faq" class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="w-full">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-16">
      
      <!-- Title -->
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">
          What we can work on together
        </h3>
      </div>

      <!-- Intro -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-6">
        <p>
          You don’t need a perfect label for your problem. Some people come with a clear question, others just feel that something isn’t working.
          Below are common themes I work with:
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3-column layout -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mb-6">

        <!-- Column 1 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
            Execution, Habits & Structure
          </p>
          <ul class="green-bullets list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-lg leading-relaxed [&>li]:my-0">
            <li>Procrastination and difficulty starting tasks</li>
            <li>Feeling overwhelmed and not knowing where to begin</li>
            <li>Building habits and routines that actually stick</li>
            <li>Staying consistent without relying on last-minute pressure</li>
            <li>Understanding how your brain works</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Column 2 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
            Clarity & Direction
          </p>
          <ul class="green-bullets list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-lg leading-relaxed [&>li]:my-0">
            <li>Feeling stuck in your studies or career</li>
            <li>Not knowing what you want or what fits you</li>
            <li>Identifying your values, interests, and priorities</li>
            <li>Making decisions with more confidence</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Column 3 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
            Patterns, Emotions & Inner Dynamics
          </p>
          <ul class="green-bullets list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-lg leading-relaxed [&>li]:my-0">
            <li>Stress, overwhelm, and emotional regulation</li>
            <li>Perfectionism and high internal pressure</li>
            <li>Repeating patterns that don’t serve you</li>
            <li>Self-doubt or feeling disconnected from yourself</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Closing text -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>
          Many of these topics are connected. For example, procrastination often links to overwhelm, unclear priorities, or deeper patterns.
          That’s why we don’t just treat symptoms — we look at the bigger picture.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How I Work -->
<section id="faq" class="py-12 bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">How I work</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <p>
      My approach is practical, structured, and tailored to you. In sessions, we combine:
      <ul class="green-bullets space-y-1 [&>li]:my-0">
        <li>reflection and honest conversation</li>
        <li>structured exercises and tools</li>
        <li>iterative and realistic experiments</li>
        <li>clear goals and (optional) homework</li>
      </ul>   
      We don't just focus on surface-level solutions, but also look at the patterns underneath - at <i>your</i> pace.
      I am supportive, but also direct. I may challenge your assumptions, but never your autonomy: 
      </br><b>you know your life best — my role is to help you see it more clearly</b>.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Coaching Trajectory -->
<section id="faq" class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">A Typical Coaching Trajectory</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg green-numbers">
    <p>
      <ol type="1">
        <li><b>Free introduction call (30 min)</b></br>We explore your situation and see if we're a good fit.</br></li>
        <li><b>Intake session</b></br>We define your goals and direction.</br></li>
        <li><b>Coaching sessions (online or in-person)</b></br>Each session focuses on what helps you move forward right now. <br>In-person sessions are possible in Almere and Amsterdam upon agreement.</br></li>
        <li><b>Review after ~5 sessions</b></br>We evaluate progress: what’s working, what’s not, and how to continue.</br></li>
        <li><b>Closing session</b></br>You leave with clarity, tools, and confidence.</br></li>
